title: State Public Health Officer Warns of Invasive Mosquitoes Detected in California (Kings County, CA)
text: ( Source : Kings County, CA ) California Department of Public Health (CDPH) Director and State Public Health Officer Dr. Karen Smith is warning Californians to protect themselves from two invasive mosquito species recently found in California .
